---
group_count: 17
atr1_unknown: 0
entries:
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk000:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 306
      - text: "我只能說你真棒啊，兄弟……\n這下子，達爾克爾的守護就能用得更順手了吧！"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk010:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 312
      - text: "要是你見到加儂那傢伙，幫我帶句話。\n「加儂……永別啦」。"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk100:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 154
      - text: "兄弟！\n你又來測試實力了嗎！？"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk110:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 257
      - text: "如果是現在的你啊……\n肯定能輕易擊敗災厄加儂！"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk200:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 154
      - text: "兄弟！\n可以幫我轉告那個小夥子嗎？"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk210:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 346
      - text: "告訴他，我小時候被別人叫做小達爾。\n那時我膽量還比他小三倍呢"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk220:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 260
      - text: "但只要努力上進、為同伴著想，\n還有多吃點美味的岩石，就能變強了……"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk230:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 139
      - text: 如果你能替我轉達給他，那可真是感激不盡……
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk300:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 211
      - text: "兄弟！\n你還記得我們兩個初次見面的時候嗎？"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk310:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 251
      - text: "真沒想到海利亞人裡，\n竟有強得能讓我以「兄弟」相稱的人……"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk320:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 323
      - text: "當時我那一臉呆滯的傻樣……\n你該不會……忘了吧？"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk400:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 206
      - text: "我說兄弟啊，\n因為你的記憶好像還是有點混亂……"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk410:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 241
      - text: "我想你或許可以讀讀那個，\n我把當初相遇的事，都記在裡頭了。"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk420:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 275
      - text: "「那個」就是我以前寫的日記，\n現在應該也還放在某處。"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk430:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 252
      - text: "看來你對我會寫日記感到很意外啊。\n總之，就去找找看如何？"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk500:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 170
      - text: "兄弟！聽好囉！\n你絕對不能告訴任何人喔。"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk510:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 223
      - text: "偷偷告訴你，其實有個怪物我怎麼也打不贏，\n實在拿牠束手無策。"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk520:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 262
      - text: "我小時候無意間踩到那傢伙的尾巴，\n結果牠先是尖叫，然後發出低鳴，接著嘶吼起來。"
  Npc_Goron_Hero_talk530:
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: auto_advance
          frames: 321
      - text: "那副齜牙咧嘴的模樣，讓我至今都還談犬色變……\n不對，應該是談虎色變……"
